videos.headline: Woods takes the pick to the house for Ole Miss
videos.description: Already up 7-0, Ole Miss strikes this time on defense when Zedrick Woods makes the pick and has nothing but green in front of him as he coasts into the end zone, making it 14-0 Rebels.
